.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-OVERVIEW 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-overview \- render project\-wide staged or live overview summaries
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util overview [\fISUBCOMMAND\fR] [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
summarize staged artifacts into one project\-wide overview.
.PP
when you want a single readout across dashboard, datasource, access, alert, and change artifacts before checking status or promoting changes.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
.B live
render the live overview by delegating to the shared status live path.
.SH EXAMPLES
.EX
grafana-util overview --dashboard-export-dir ./dashboards/raw --alert-export-dir ./alerts --desired-file ./desired.json --output table
.EE
.EX
grafana-util overview --source-bundle ./sync-source-bundle.json --target-inventory ./target-inventory.json --availability-file ./availability.json --mapping-file ./mapping.json --output text
.EE
.EX
grafana-util overview live --profile prod --output yaml
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgrafana-util\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-status\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-change\fR(1),
\fBgrafana-util-snapshot\fR(1)
